{"tid":1007104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"赤柱男子潛水遇溺昏迷　卜公碼頭救起送院不治","createTime":"2019-02-03T13:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T14:32:12.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cdadb63d41e6d72191d5b6b68c0d4080fa4b93ce","tid":1007104,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T13:44:25.000Z","msg":"今（3日）晚上8時許，赤柱一名男子與朋友下海潛水時，約兩分鐘後他失去蹤影，朋友及後發現他遇溺，立即將他救上船及報警。他被送往赤柱大街的卜公碼頭上岸，當時已陷入昏迷，由救護車送住東區醫院搶救，惟返魂乏術，終告不治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/291340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F291340&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToPsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=3ada3d4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/291340</a>"},{"pid":"6c41fc973340e944bd7f11fe5bba6b182a37e034","tid":1007104,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"7月14<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}